<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
The flustered sentinel looks at you expectantly.
Deliver the fur blanket and purified water to the flustered sentinel.
Normally I would not think to make a request of the allies of Ronka, but this is an emergency.
One of our sisters is in labor. Would you help us make ready for the delivery?
I have asked Olmet to prepare a blanket for the child, and Ciuille fresh water.
Time is of the essence. Go and speak with Olmet and Ciuille. They will have what we need.
Ah, I was told someone would be coming. Here─a blanket of our finest fur. Go on, now. They will be waiting.
It is time, then? I finished purifying the water but moments ago. The child's ears must be cleansed before first hearkening to the call of the woods.
I will not keep you. The others are waiting for that blanket.
Be careful not to spill the water.
Do you have the blanket and water?
Good, good. With this, everything is in order.
It has been far too long since any of our sisters has given birth.
You honor us with your assistance. Would that we could allow you to meet the child once born.

To ensure their safety, it is strictly forbidden for any save the wet nurse and immediate family to see them. Even should the opportunity never arise, make no mistake: the child will hear of your deeds. You have my word on that.
